data.description: DELIGHTFUL 2 Bedroom, 2 Bathroom home situated on TWO LOTS. Property is 160 feet wide and 125 feet deep. There is a 24x13  attached Garage as well as a 16x20 detached garage/shed (steel with high windloads) with overhead door. NO HOA. This light and bright home features a Living Room/ Dining Room combo, well equipped Kitchen and enclosed porch. The spacious kitchen has an oven/range, refrigerator, dishwasher, disposal and space for a table. The Master Bedroom suite has a walk in closet and private bathroom with walk in shower. There is an additional generous sized bedroom and the guest bathroom has a tub/shower combo and granite counter on the vanity. The living room is open to the 16x10 porch enclosed with windows. French doors lead from the enclosed porch to the spacious backyard with patio covered with pergola and 8x6 shed. Table and chairs on the patio as well as the garden bench convey with the house. Other features include screened front entry, luxury vinyl plank flooring throughout the house except for laminate in the Kitchen, metal roof. Utilities are public water and sewer. Minutes from shopping, dining, medical care, entertainment, waterfront parks, boat ramps, fishing piers.
